## ğŸ‰ Email Verification & Onboarding System (Oct 25, 2025)

### Complete User Activation Flow
```
Register â†’ Email Sent â†’ Verify Email â†’ Pending Admin â†’ Approved â†’ Active
   âœ…         ğŸ“§            âœ…              â³            ğŸ‘¨â€ğŸ’¼        ğŸ‰
